<item>
            <title>[LU-4672] sanity-hsm test_55: request is not STARTED</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4672</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/31d35b1a-9d6c-11e3-90b5-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/31d35b1a-9d6c-11e3-90b5-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_55 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;request on 0x400000401:0x1bc:0x0 is not STARTED on mds1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There have been several similar failures over the past few weeks.&lt;br/&gt;
Info required for matching: sanity-hsm 55&lt;/p&gt;</description>
